  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "dKgRd5wbPT/nf0+Cr3CYajUZaCo=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:48.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "The v6 Reactor introduced three subgraph types: the reactor subgraph (`/graphql/r`) for drives, documents, sync, and subscriptions; auto-generated document-model subgraphs (`/graphql/<model-name>`) with namespaced queries/mutations per registered model; and custom user-defined subgraphs. Document-model subgraphs auto-generate `document(identifier)`, `documents(paging)`, `findDocuments(search)`, `documentChildren(parentIdentifier)`, `createDocument(name)`, and per-operation mutations (e.g., `addTodoItem(docId, input)`) with async variants. Legacy strand-based sync (`registerPullResponderListener`, `system.sync.strands`) was replaced with channel-based sync (`touchChannel`, `pollSyncEnvelopes`) and GraphQL subscriptions (`documentChanges`).",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:48.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:48.000Z"
    }
  },
